Subject: System Administrators not Syncing from Defined AD Group
Description:
Under System Configuration > System Settings > Active Directory Authentication, we have successfully enabled AD authentication and confirmed that it is working. However, the Active Directory Adminimstrators Group Sync does not seem to be working. Is there a specific format that I need to define the group as? There is an account in the group.

The group is GSADF1P_0000iqa_CoSoSysEPP-NPASuperAdmins_P
Solution_Comment__c: There was a mistake regarding the configuration. The case can be  closed now after resolving the configuration.
